            </button>
            <span class="overlay-title">Ratings &amp; Community</span>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay-body">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How does the rating system work?<img
                        src="../assets/icons/icon_left_chevron.svg" class="faq-chevron icon-muted"
                        style="transform:rotate(-90deg)" alt=""></div>
                <div class="faq-a">After each completed trip, both driver and passenger can leave a rating. Ratings are
                    averaged over time and visible on your public profile.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What happens if I get a bad rating?<img
                        src="../assets/icons/icon_left_chevron.svg" class="faq-chevron icon-muted"
                        style="transform:rotate(-90deg)" alt=""></div>
